restlib

Class RequestPreconditionsBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • restlib.RequestPreconditionsBuilder

  • @NotThreadSafe
public final class RequestPreconditionsBuilder
extends Object
    A builder for generating RequestPrecondition instances. RequestBuilder instances can be reused; it is safe to call build() multiple times to build multiple RequestPreconditions instances.
